title: Bobby’s 36 Hours With COVID Exposure And Capitol Protests + Raymundo Almost Got Arrested + Eddie Did Something He Swore He’d Never Do!
itunes:title: Bobby’s 36 Hours With COVID Exposure And Capitol Protests + Raymundo Almost Got Arrested + Eddie Did Something He Swore He’d Never Do!
description:
Bobby tells us about his last 36 hours...gives his thoughts on the Capitol protests from yesterday. Bobby gets Raymundo to share a story about his honeymoon where he almost got busted by police. Eddie reveals something to us that he did over the break he swore he’d NEVER do. Plus, Bobby also addresses a concern from Eddie about a new country duo who he thinks is ripping off their look!
